flowchart TB

A[Transaction Event\nInbound payment or transfer]
B[Data Ingestion Layer\nREST upload plus replay trigger]
C[Streaming and Processing Layer\nFastAPI plus WebSocket live feed]
D[Feature Extraction\nVelocity Amount Time Graph India context]
E[AI Fraud Model\nXGBoost fraud probability]
F[Graph Intelligence\nFund flow Ring Mule signals]
G[Risk Scoring Engine\nAggregate score and threshold calibration]
H{Risk Level?}
I[Allow or Monitor\nPass-through]
J[Flag High Risk\nCreate live alert]
K[Risk Propagation Engine\nSpread risk across linked accounts]
L[Investigation Workspace\nCase management plus freeze simulation]
M[Explainability and Case Report\nTop factors Evidence Confidence]
N[Analyst Dashboard Output\nLive feed Alerts KPIs]
O[Model Feedback Loop\nAnalyst verdicts plus score refresh]

A --> B --> C --> D --> E --> G --> H
D --> F --> G
H -->|Low or Medium| I --> N
H -->|High| J --> K --> L --> M --> N
N --> O
O -.Continuous improvement.-> E

